               <msContents>
                  <summary>Manuscript containing three taz̲kiras in Persian and Urdu: Ikhlāṣ Chand's <title>Hamīsha Bahār</title>, Ḥazīn's <title>Taz̲kira-yi Muʿāṣirīn</title>, and Qā'im's <title>Makhzan-i Nikāt</title>.</summary>
